    <mxCell id="grasp_note" value="GRASP Patterns Summary&#xa;&#xa;Controller: ProjectController, DiagramController, AIController, MainWindow&#xa;  Handle system events; delegate work to domain objects.&#xa;&#xa;Information Expert: Project, UMLDiagram, UMLClass, Attribute, Method,&#xa;  Relationship, ChatMessage, EvaluationReport&#xa;  Own and manage their information.&#xa;&#xa;Creator: DiagramController creates UMLDiagram. UMLDiagram (Composition)&#xa;  owns UMLClass + Relationship. UMLClass (Composition) owns Attribute + Method.&#xa;&#xa;Pure Fabrication: All Repository Impls, LLMAPIEngine, JavaCodeParser,&#xa;  DiagramExportService, SpeechToTextServiceImpl, DatabaseManager.&#xa;  Artificial classes supporting low coupling and high cohesion.&#xa;&#xa;Low Coupling: Controllers depend only on interfaces, never on concretions.&#xa;&#xa;High Cohesion: Each class has exactly one well-defined responsibility.&#xa;&#xa;Polymorphism: 7 interfaces with interchangeable implementations.&#xa;  abstract Relationship with 3 concrete subtypes." style="text;html=1;strokeColor=#CC6600;fillColor=#ffe6cc;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=10;rounded=1;fontSize=11;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="2760" y="300" width="430" height="450" as="geometry"/></mxCell>

    

    
